// CodeBlock
// Syntax-highlighted code block with a copy-to-clipboard button.
// Supports dark and light themes via CSS class toggling.

FUNCTION handleCopy()
  Copies the code string to the clipboard.
  Sets a "copied" state flag for 2 seconds to show feedback, then resets it.

---

FUNCTION CodeBlock(props) -> ReactNode                                    EXPORT
  Renders a pre/code block with the provided code string.
  Shows a copy button in the top-right corner; button label changes to "Copied!" briefly after clicking.
  Applies syntax highlighting styles based on the active theme.
